{"tid":2141340,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（亞洲軍備競賽）韓國確定買F35B 並且有計劃興建航母","createTime":"2020-08-05T14:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T10:42:03.000Z","uid":295230,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"25d75d46983de743d6f22eac65ed98c849aa7269","tid":2141340,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9NF1n86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9NF1n86.jpg&h=388a1808&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.navyrecognition.com/index.php/news/defence-news/2020/august/8807-south-korea-navy-recent-f-35b-order-confirms-plans-to-get-new-aircraft-carrier.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.navyrecognition.com%2Findex.php%2Fnews%2Fdefence-news%2F2020%2Faugust%2F8807-south-korea-navy-recent-f-35b-order-confirms-plans-to-get-new-aircraft-carrier.html&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2FzH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=eb9e77d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.navyrecognition.com/index.php/news/defence-news/2020/august/8807-south-korea-navy-recent-f-35b-order-confirms-plans-to-get-new-aircraft-carrier.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單總結下，就係韓國已向美國增訂20架F35B戰機，F35B係垂直下降版本，主要係比美軍陸戰隊係兩棲突擊艦上面使用，美海軍版本係F35C。但F35B都同時比英國，義大利同日本使用，當作佢地既艦載機使用。<br />\n<br />\n而係幾個月前也有消息流出，話韓國正準備興建1至2艘既中型既航母，類似英國既伊利沙伯女王號，大既為7萬吨，可以載有32架F35B戰機，如果成事韓國將成為亞洲第四個擁有航母既國家（中國，日本，印度，而秦國果架就算撚數）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uaiKkXo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuaiKkXo.jpg&h=41c30ce7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CxCCFXs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCxCCFXs.jpg&h=f837d10f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國係2014年訂購左首批40架陸基用既F35A戰機，首批次已經係上年接收，同時韓國都係上年再次向美增購20架F35A戰機，計埋呢次20架F35B戰機，韓國將會擁有80架第五代隱影戰機，軍力係亞洲甚至放眼世界都係數一數二<br />\n<br />\n韓國，日本，中國同印度近年不斷擴充軍力，已見亞洲軍備競賽既初形<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5481e2d26186f1c3ae3e1343dcf901db0f1906d1","tid":2141340,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:56:29.000Z","msg":"補多個source:<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20200805006600325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.yna.co.kr%2Fview%2FAEN20200805006600325&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2FzH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=e00b682b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20200805006600325</a>"},{"pid":"3461cf158d71da555ab463b307ccde88f7a3cc06","tid":2141340,"uid":98242,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:57:47.000Z","msg":"奶得咁勁做唔買強國飛機，好失禮咩？"},{"pid":"feac818488f58a6817e00583f19eff0c77d735cd","tid":2141340,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:58:03.000Z","msg":"十八路諸侯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df149c8de9b2320010105fe948909dde2274631d","tid":2141340,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:00:29.000Z","msg":"同場加映：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>韓軍公開多種新型武器研發項目</strong> <br />\n韓聯社泰安8月5日<br />\n<br />\n韓國國防科學研究所3日在位於忠清南道泰安郡的安興綜合試驗場舉 行聯合演示和展覽活動紀念建所50週年，並發布正在推進的研發項目。<br />\n<br />\n軍方表示，正在開 發搭載超小型合成孔徑雷達（SAR）的偵察衛星，加快研發為設計隱形無人戰鬥機（UCAV ）的核心技術。<br />\n<br />\n 據國防科學研究所介紹，從去年底開始研發超小型合成孔徑雷達衛星體系的地面試驗模式 ，爭取2023年11月前完成開發。搭載該雷達的衛星呈長方形，長3米，寬70釐米，重量為 66公斤以下。前置雷達，後置太陽能電池板，分辨率達到1米級，即可在510千米高空不分 晝夜、全天候觀測地面上1米大小的物體。研究所方面指出，若有32顆搭載超小型合成孔 徑雷達的衛星，可以每30分鐘間隔偵察韓半島周邊地區。<br />\n<br />\n 研究所還首次披露正在研發為設計隱形無人戰鬥機的核心技術。主要研究內容包括無人戰 鬥機機身設計、提高隱形功能的電波吸收結構、無尾翼飛行控制技術。該無人戰鬥機長 14.8米，翼展10.4米，軍方的目標是爭取戰鬥機能在10千米上空以0.5馬赫的速度續航3小 時。 研究所還在開發中大型無人潛艇體系的核心技術。預計掌握相關技術後，韓軍不必向北方 界線一帶等地派遣官兵，可以利用無人潛艇遠程監視和偵察朝軍潛艇等武器。<br />\n<br />\n此外，軍方 將開發20噸級超高速艇，計畫明年4月前完成開發。"},{"pid":"5b2b11b16ec0f671539abebc567c1810f6f50702","tid":2141340,"uid":295230,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"3461cf158d71da555ab463b307ccde88f7a3cc06","tid":2141340,"uid":98242,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:57:47.000Z","msg":"奶得咁勁做唔買強國飛機，好失禮咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:01:17.000Z","msg":"你估韓國真係好信中國咩～而且仲有隻北韓係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65fc1e613096c540d93c39c90cca343d2acc1a3","tid":2141340,"uid":212796,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5b2b11b16ec0f671539abebc567c1810f6f50702","tid":2141340,"uid":295230,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"3461cf158d71da555ab463b307ccde88f7a3cc06","tid":2141340,"uid":98242,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:57:47.000Z","msg":"奶得咁勁做唔買強國飛機，好失禮咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:01:17.000Z","msg":"你估韓國真係好信中國咩～而且仲有隻北韓係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:03:26.000Z","msg":"成班打手今朝笑尻袁伯伯講七眼依家失晒蹤"},{"pid":"ebf0d94dd7aaeb7553e7546ae7531299f2819557","tid":2141340,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:03:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01d4ed7254711546ba69ba10254b37fd87f86148","tid":2141340,"uid":295230,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"3461cf158d71da555ab463b307ccde88f7a3cc06","tid":2141340,"uid":98242,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:57:47.000Z","msg":"奶得咁勁做唔買強國飛機，好失禮咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:05:29.000Z","msg":"再講，中國有咩機可以上艦？果架超重既J15定係都市傳說J31<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729410de168149c19f4cf812f66c02bdf78ae6f1","tid":2141340,"uid":295230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d65fc1e613096c5